description:
This Tender Notice issued by Tai Tarian as a single stage procurement exercise, in accordance with the below-threshold requirements of the Procurement Act 2023.
Tai Tarian is seeking to award a Contract to a single Supplier, for Enterprise Network Modernisation & Multi-Site Infrastructure Support. The scope of the Contract requires the Supplier to:
-	Deliver a modern, secure, multi-site network infrastructure design;
-	Provide hardware and software recommendations;
